Package uk.ac.ebi.gxa.loader.handler.sdrf

Class Summary
AtlasLoadingAssayHandler A dedicated handler for creating assay objects and storing them in the cache whenever a new assay node is encountered.
AtlasLoadingDerivedArrayDataMatrixHandler A dedicated handler that parses expression data from a specified data matrix file, referenced in the SDRF.
AtlasLoadingHybridizationHandler A dedicated handler for creating assay objects and storing them in the cache whenever a new hybridization node is encountered.
AtlasLoadingSourceHandler A dedicated handler for creating sample objects and storing them in the cache whenever a new source node is encountered.
